org.projectspinoza.twitterswissarmyknife

Class CLIDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.projectspinoza.twitterswissarmyknife.CLIDriver

  • public class CLIDriver
extends java.lang.Object
    CLIDriver contains all of the command line logic e.g. identifying the command, executing and returning its result. it also shows the rateLimitStatus e.g. the remaining twitter API calls for the executed command.
    Version:
    v1.0
    Author:
    org.projectspinoza
